<span class="label">ACM News</span>
<h2>Why China is Betting Big on Chiplets</h2>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By MIT Technology Review
<br/>
February 7, 2024<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
